      "node ./scripts/prettier.js --pre",
      "git add"
    ],
    "{site,components}/**/*.less": [
      "stylelint --syntax less",
      "node ./scripts/prettier.js --pre",
      "git add"
    ],
    "components/*/demo/*.md": [
      "npm run lint-staged:demo"
    ]
  },
  "sideEffects": [
    "dist/*",
    "es/**/style/*",
    "lib/**/style/*",
    "*.less"
  ]
}
;
